<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288992>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 31. Lasioseius parberlesei. Female: Specimens from West Bengal, India: 23. Dorsal shield; 24. Tritosternum; 25. Ventral shields; 26. Peritrematic plate; 27. Spermatheca; 28. Chelicera; 29. Epistome; 30. Hypostome; 31. Genu, tibia and tarsus of leg IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288993>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32 – 39. Lasioseius parberlesei. Male: 32. Paratype dorsal shield. Additional specimens from West Bengal, India: 33. Dorsal shield; 34. Tritosternum; 35. Ventral shields; 36. Spermadactyl; 37. Epistome; 38. Hypostome; 39. Genu, tibia and tarsus of male leg IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

